                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xingshuiqy/">荥水晴阳</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-04-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">有些论证觉得逻辑不够严密，有些则让人拍案叫绝。还有很多，需要拿来自省。。常看常新！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

